---
<div class="landing-section">
  <h2>Quick start</h2>
  <p class="subtitle">Four commands. That's it.</p>

  <div class="terminal">
    <div><span class="comment"># Initialise any git repo</span></div>
    <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">cd</span> your-project</div>
    <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx fleetspark init</span></div>
    <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><span class="comment"># Plan your work (this machine becomes the commander)</span></div>
    <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx fleetspark command --plan</span> "Add OAuth, fix rate limiter, update docs"</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><span class="comment"># On any other machine</span></div>
    <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx fleetspark ship --join</span> git@github.com:you/your-project.git</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><span class="comment"># Watch the live dashboard (or check fleet status --json from anywhere)</span></div>
    <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx fleetspark dashboard</span></div>
  </div>
</div>
